Docs.remarks:

  The following example shows the creation of a ScrollView with a large  in it.


var stack = new StackLayout();

for (int i = 0; i < 100; i++)
{
    stack.Children.Add(new Button { Text = "Button " + i });
}

MainPage = new ContentPage
{
    Content = new ScrollView { Content = stack }
};

      Note: application developers should not nest one  within another. Additionally, they should refrain from nesting them other elements that can scroll, such as .

